{"tid":1471864,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[慎入][傷口圖] 荃灣被斬示威者送院時傷勢圖","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T02:57:56.000Z","uid":186908,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9dddfae5e77f85458c08a192935082787d680a73","tid":1471864,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:35:33.000Z","msg":"【1900】有已核實身分的醫護人員聯絡本頻道，提供兩張荃灣被斬示威者（圖）送院時傷勢的照片。<br />\n<br />\n該名醫護呼籲，希望市民認清什麼才是真正的暴力，又稱不會指責昨晚在機場集會動手的示威者，因為兩個月以來不少示威者都被警察或者黑社會攻擊致受傷，而傷勢之重，與昨日於機場被打的疑似公安及環時記者根本無從比較，「好多人已經為呢件事付出好多，現在唔係指責或者割席嘅時候」。<br />\n<br />\n以下為傷勢照片，或會引起嚴重不安，查看前請務必做好心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慎入！血腥警報！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n左腳傷勢圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0k1UL0.jpg&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=fcdfa0b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n右手傷勢圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoeH3751.jpg&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=b44fe6ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上見到有人開post : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156141676215286?sfns=xmwa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fwesterndistrict%2Fpermalink%2F10156141676215286%3Fsfns%3Dxmwa&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=ce72e218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156141676215286?sfns=xmwa</a>"},{"pid":"b8c6071795fb8bf3cf97c60edd68aa0393762518","tid":1471864,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11: